questions in crypto regulation</a> are:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Will US regulators (and particularly =
the SEC) remain as hostile to crypto as they are right now, or will the US =
become more crypto-friendly through some combination of congressional legis=
lation, court rulings that go against the SEC, personnel changes at regulat=
ors, etc.?</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">If the US=C2=A0<em>does=
=C2=A0</em>remain super hostile to crypto, will that be bad for crypto=C2=
=A0<em>globally</em>, or will it just mean that crypto becomes a non-US thi=
ng? In general, US regulators and prosecutors are very=C2=A0good at using t=
he power of the US government and the reach of the dollar system to impose =
US decisions on global finance. If you are a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.b=
loombergbusiness.com/click/32851551.261423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNv=
bS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTQtMDctMDEvYm5wLWNvbXBsaWFuY2Utb2ZmaWNlcnMtd2V=
yZS1maW5lLXdpdGgtc29tZS1ub24tY29tcGxpYW5jZT9jbXBpZD1CQkQwOTI3MjNfTU9ORVlTVF=
VGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzA5M=
jcmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBf96c0df4" itemp=
rop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color:=
 #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; borde=
r-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc=
;">  French bank providing financing to a Cuban company</a>, and the US doe=
sn=E2=80=99t like that, it will stop you. But crypto is different! Crypto i=
s anonymous and borderless and irreversible and censorship-resistant; if th=
e US decides to ban crypto then it can maybe (maybe) cut US citizens off fr=
om the joys of crypto, but it can=E2=80=99t interfere with crypto=E2=80=99s=
 global growth. Or that is an idea anyway.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This year US <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloo=
mbergbusiness.com/click/32851551.261423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9=
