solid; background-color: #ccc;">  regulators</a> have brought <a href=3D"ht=
tps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32851551.261423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3c=
uYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDYtMDYvdGhlLXNlYy1jb21lcy=
